摘要
I
摘要
党的十九大报告提出乡村振兴战略,旨在实现农业强、农村美、农民富的乡村
全面振兴。乡村教育振兴作为乡村振兴战略的重要组成部分,对于乡村经济发展、
乡村社会的转型、村民整体文化素质的提升以及乡村创业和创新能力的提升都发挥
着至关重要的作用。随着国家对乡村教育重视程度的不断提高,中国乡村教育获得
了长足的发展。但是,在一些贫困的乡村地区,乡村教育仍存在着诸多问题和困境,
在一定程度上制约着乡村振兴战略的实施。因此,研究乡村振兴战略框架下的乡村
小学教育发展具有重要的理论和现实意义。
本文以 JX 县乡村小学为研究对象,在阐明乡村振兴战略及乡村教育内涵的基础
上,以资源配置理论和人力资本理论为指导,运用文献分析法、问卷调查法和访谈
法,分析 JX 县乡村小学教育的发展现状,探索 JX 县乡村小学教育发展中存在的问
题,发现在教育资源配置、教师队伍建设、乡村学校教育发展思路方面的问题阻碍
了 JX 县乡村小学教育的发展,其原因在于:乡村地理环境的制约、乡村社会环境的
限制、乡村家庭教育的忽视、乡村落后经济的阻碍、乡村小学生生源的锐减、教育
资源分配不均以及教育经费政策的束缚。针对问题提出对策:强化政府在乡村小学
教育中的主导作用;注重学校对乡村振兴的关键作用;发挥社会作用帮助留守儿童
健康成长;发挥乡村经济对乡村教育的推动作用。期待通过此研究,能为 JX 县乡村
小学教育的发展提供参考。
关键词 乡村振兴;乡村小学教育;教育均衡;教育资源配置;师资队伍建设


Abstract
III
Abstract
The report of the 19th National Congress of the Communist Party of China (CPC) put
forward the rural revitalization strategy, which aims to realize the comprehensive
revitalization of rural areas with strong agriculture, beautiful rural areas and rich farmers.
As an important part of rural revitalization strategy, rural education revitalization plays a
vital role in rural economic development, rural social transformation, improvement of
villagers' overall cultural quality and improvement of rural entrepreneurship and
innovation ability. With the increasing emphasis of the country on rural education, China's
rural education has made considerable progress. However, in some poor rural areas, there
are still many problems and difficulties in rural education, which restrict the
implementation of rural revitalization strategy to some extent. Therefore, the study of rural
primary school education development under the framework of rural revitalization
strategy has important theoretical and practical significance.
Taking JX county rural primary school as the research object, on the basis of
clarifying the country revitalization strategy and the connotation of rural education,
according to the theory of the allocation of resources and human capital theory as the
instruction, using literature analysis, questionnaire investigation and interview method,
analyzing the development of the JX county rural elementary education, exploring the
problems existing in the rural primary school education development of JX county, found
the problems in the allocation of education resources, the teachers troop construction and
rural school education development ideas hindered the development of JX county rural
primary school education, its reason is: the constraints of rural geographical environment
and rural social environment, the neglect of family education in rural areas, the obstacles
to backward rural economy, the sharp decrease in the enrollment of rural primary school
students, uneven distribution of educational resources and the restrictions of educational
expenditure policy. Countermeasures are put forward: strengthening the leading role of
government in rural primary school education; paying attention to the key role of schools
in rural revitalization; playing a social role in helping left-behind children grow up
healthily; bring into play the promoting role of rural economy to rural education. It is
expected that this research can provide reference for the development of rural primary
school education in JX County.


